  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Introduction</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a survival horror game set in a haunting school environment.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay Description</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player controls a girl exploring different locations within the school to find memory fragments. With each fragment she collects, her lost memories slowly return, revealing more about what happened that day. Keep her safe from hidden threats and survive to uncover the whole truth.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Controls</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arrow keys: Move<br>Z: Interact<br>Shift + Arrow keys: Dash<br>ESC: Open Menu<br>Alt + Enter: Window Mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Introduction</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a survival horror game set in a haunting school environment.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay Description</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The player controls a girl exploring different locations within the school to find memory fragments. With each fragment she collects, her lost memories slowly return, revealing more about what happened that day. Keep her safe from hidden threats and survive to uncover the whole truth.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Controls</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arrow keys: Move<br>Z: Interact<br>Shift + Arrow keys: Dash<br>ESC: Open Menu<br>Alt + Enter: Window Mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
